### List games
GET http://localhost:3000/games

### List games with pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/games?limit=10&offset=0

### Create a game
POST http://localhost:3000/games
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rows": 8,
  "columns": 8
}

### Create a game (minimum size)
POST http://localhost:3000/games
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rows": 2,
  "columns": 2
}

### Create a game (maximum size)
POST http://localhost:3000/games
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rows": 100,
  "columns": 100
}

### Create a game (invalid size)
POST http://localhost:3000/games
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rows": 1,
  "columns": 2
}

### Get a game by id (replace UUID)
GET http://localhost:3000/games/440037e3-f3b3-4e59-93cd-27ab2f0ab142

### Reveal a cell
POST http://localhost:3000/games/440037e3-f3b3-4e59-93cd-27ab2f0ab142/moves
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "x": 0,
  "y": 0,
  "action": "REVEAL"
}

### Flag a cell
POST http://localhost:3000/games/440037e3-f3b3-4e59-93cd-27ab2f0ab142/moves
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "x": 0,
  "y": 0,
  "action": "FLAG"
}

### Unflag a cell
POST http://localhost:3000/games/440037e3-f3b3-4e59-93cd-27ab2f0ab142/moves
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "x": 0,
  "y": 0,
  "action": "UNFLAG"
}
